'''subsidy_multiplier''' is a variable of Openttd.cfg file:

Sets the bonus multiplier for subsidies offered in the game.<br><br>
0 = 1.5x the normal rate<br>
1 = 2.0x the normal rate<br>
2 = 3.0x the normal rate<br>
3 = 4.0x the normal rate<br>

<pre>
[difficulty]
subsidy_multiplier = 2
</pre>

'''Valid options:''' [ 0 | 1 | 2 | 3 ]

'''Default:''' 2


